title: Too Faced Boudoir Eyes Soft and Sexy Eye Shadow Collection, 0.39 Ounce
description: Why we love it: our new hand-picked collection of eye shadows create looks for the bedroom and beyond. Along with four boudoir-worthy colors, we created five new shades just for this palette for a total of nine soft and sexy colors.

title: NARS Shimmer Eyeshadow, Nepal
description: Longwearing, crease resistant color in sheer wearable formulas. All NARS eyeshadows can be applied sheer or layered for a more dramatic effect. These richly pigmented powders blend effortlessly and can also be used wet for precisely lining the eyes.
